cast.overview: A New York stockbroker refuses to cooperate in a large securities fraud case involving corruption on Wall Street, corporate banking world and mob infiltration. Based on Jordan Belfort's autobiography.
cast.title: The Wolf of Wall Street

details.biography:
​From Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia.  

Joseph Zaso (born on November 20, 1970 in Queens, New York) is an American actor and filmmaker.

He is a b-movie regular and has been involved in the low budget science fiction and horror industry since 1990. Zaso, an avid bodybuilder, is usually cast as husky villains.
